        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-me&#34;&gt;About Me
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;ü•∑ A self-taught, semi-wild programmer who came into tech a bit unconventionally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚å®Ô∏è Started out in game development, but curious about many fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üéí Spent years in school &amp;ndash; only to realize most of what I know came from self-learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üçµ Used to love fitness and travel. These days, I‚Äôm all about the cozy indoor life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üê± Forever an animal lover.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìö  Forever a book lover.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-this-site&#34;&gt;About This Site
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;content&#34;&gt;Content
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Back when I was more of an artsy type, I enjoyed sharing bits of my personal life. These days, I focus on documenting my learning and work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-name-nullshow&#34;&gt;The Name: Nullshow
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;null&lt;/strong&gt; stands for ‚Äúempty‚Äù‚Äîa reflection of how I view life, and a reminder to always keep a beginner‚Äôs mindset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;show&lt;/strong&gt;  sounds like part of my Chinese name. The pronunciation of &lt;strong&gt;Nullshow&lt;/strong&gt; is close to a childhood nickname, which brings back memories of carefree days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;illustrations&#34;&gt;Illustrations
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;All &lt;strong&gt;category&lt;/strong&gt; illustrations come from Feng Zikai (1898‚Äì1975), a pioneer of Chinese comic art. His works are drawn from everyday life‚Äîsimple, expressive, and full of childlike charm. He was from the same hometown as me. Using his art is both a tribute and a reminder to stay mindful of the beauty in daily life, beyond study and work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;gratitude&#34;&gt;Gratitude
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;This site was built with inspiration and silent help from many brilliant minds online. It‚Äôs made me truly appreciate the power of open-source and sharing. In this era of technological revolution, AI is making everything simpler and faster. I hope I‚Äôm not just swept along by the tide &amp;ndash; but riding the wave with intention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thanks for joining me on this journey in such an exciting time.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
